# Pagination 分页

用于数据列表或表格的分页切换。

<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref } from 'vue'

const page = ref(1)
</script>

## 基础用法
### 分页导航
在多页数据间切换。
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="PaginationPaginationDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const page = ref(1)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxPagination
      v-model:current-page="page"
      :total="120"
      :page-size="10"
      show-info
      show-first-last
    />
  </template>
---
:::
## API
### Props
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: currentPage
    type: number
    default: '1'
    description: 当前页
  - name: pageSize
    type: number
    default: '10'
    description: 每页数量
  - name: total
    type: number
    default: '0'
    description: 总数量
  - name: totalPages
    type: number
    default: '-'
    description: 显式总页数；未提供 total 时使用
  - name: prevIcon
    type: string
    default: "'chevron-left'"
    description: 上一页图标
  - name: nextIcon
    type: string
    default: "'chevron-right'"
    description: 下一页图标
  - name: showInfo
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 显示总量信息
  - name: showFirstLast
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 显示首末页按钮
---
::

